        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a pure computational kernel implementing GEOS-Chem 2012 sea salt emission scheme with observational constraints. NO error checking, validation, or infrastructure concerns. Host model must ensure all inputs are valid before calling.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
